cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "AOS Recipes — Greek pharmaceutical recipe corpus"
abstract: >
  193 QC-complete Greek pharmaceutical recipe records extracted from
  Dioscorides (Books 1 and 2), Aëtius of Amida (Books 1 and 16), and
  Paul of Aegina (Book 7.20), with normalized entities, an ingredient
  lexicon, Apriori co-occurrence analysis, and a mirrored quantity-gold
  overlay layer. v1.0 is the canonical snapshot ingested into the
  Claude cowork scholarly revision workflow.
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Coughlin
    given-names: Sean
    email: coughlin@flu.cas.cz
    affiliation: Institute of Philosophy, Czech Academy of Sciences
version: 1.0.0
date-released: "2026-06-07"
repository-code: "https://github.com/alchemiesofscent/aos-recipes"
license: CC-BY-4.0
keywords:
